        <h1>Potato Tikki</h1>
        
        <div class="recipe-details">
        <img src="potato-tikki.jpg" alt="Potato Tikki" class="recipe-image">
            <div class="ingredients">
                <h2>Ingredients:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>3 potatoes, boiled and mashed</li>
                    <li>1/2 cup green peas, boiled</li>
                    <li>1 tsp cumin powder</li>
                    <li>1 tsp chaat masala</li>
                    <li>Salt to taste</li>
                    <li>Oil for frying</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <br>
            <div class="instructions">
                <h2>Instructions:</h2>
                <ol>
                    <li>Mix mashed potatoes, peas, cumin powder, chaat masala, and salt together.</li>
                    <li>Shape into small patties.</li>
                    <li>Heat oil in a pan and fry the tikkis until golden brown on both sides.</li>
                    <li>Serve hot with chutney or ketchup.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
